Title: There's Only One Second Best
Plot: Alex finds himself in a much desired stress-free situation after a demotion makes him the third-string quarterback. However, after being forced to hang out with the special teams, he is desperate to reclaim his lost position.
ParentalRatingReason: Sex scenes, drug use & content that may offend
GuestStars: James Cade, Moshana Halbert, Meghan Heffern, Omari Newton, Rob Ramsay, Kwasi Songui
